        },
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Hariga-Origa in Windurst Waters at (F-8).\n2. You will be given the [Key Item] Note from Hariga-Origa, and asked to deliver it to Ipupu.\n   - Ipupu is located in West Sarutabaruta (I-8/J-8), near the entrance to Windurst Waters.\n3. She will accept the item and in return give you the [Key Item] Note from Ipupu to deliver to Hariga-Origa.\n4. After delivering the note, you will complete the quest and receive your rewards.',
