        walkthrough = 'Note: Completion of Reap What You Sow is not required to activate this quest, and it cannot be initiated while this quest is active or if Making the Grade is active.\n1. Speak to Mashuu-Ajuu (K-6) and then Paku-Nakku to begin this quest.\n2. Next, speak to Maabu-Sonbu, Port Windurst (E-7) (Home Point #1).\n3. Grab some Sickles and head to Pashhow Marshlands (via Derfland).\n4. Harvest at the ??? at (E-5) to obtain the Blazing Peppers.\n   - These can also be purchased on the Auction House.\n5. Trade the peppers to Paku-Nakku.\n6. Talk to Pechiru-Mashiru.\n7. Talk to Paku-Nakku again.\n   - Choose the prompt "The automaton butler did it!"\n8. Finally, speak to Pechiru-Mashiru for your reward.',
