        walkthrough = '1. Zone after completing the previous quest.\n2. Speak to Kohlo-Lakolo for a storytelling sequence to begin this quest.\n   - If you already have the Old ring, you\'ll skip ahead to the final cut scene.\n3. Head to Castle Oztroja and head to the door at (I-8) on the first map.\n4. Using the handles in front of the door, intentionally activate the trap door and fall down it.\n5. Check the Blank Target in this room to receive an Old ring.\n6. Return to Kohlo-Lakolo who will send you to the "House of the Hero" Windurst Walls (G-3) for your reward.\n   - If you take too long to return the ring the quest will end when you return to Kohlo-Lakolo and you will not have to go to the "House of the Hero" afterwards. The quest is still considered complete.\n7. Zone and return to Kohlo-Lakolo to receive your reward.',
