        fame = 'Windurst',
        fame_level = nil,
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. You cannot start this quest if you have another Weapon Skill Quest active. You must return to the person that gave said quest and quit it to start another.\n2. Speaking with Kuroido-Moido will grant you the key item Weapons Training Guide as well as the Club of Trials. You will need to break the latent on the Club of Trials before completing the rest of the quest.\n      - Breaking the Latent\n3. Trade the Club of Trials back to Kuroido-Moido. This will give you the key item Map to the Annals of Truth. You will be instructed to travel to Ro\'Maeve.\n4. Take Silent Oil and head to Ro\'Maeve.\n5. Inside Ro\'Maeve, go down the northeastern stairs and turn immediately east. Go through the hallway to the right. Turn left, drop down the ledge and go through the door to the northeast. Turn left, head up the stairs to the north at (K-8). Follow the path northwest until you come to a northeast path through an open doorway at (J-8).\n   - Alternatively, if you have the Survival Guide warp or are starting from the Hall of the Gods zone just run down the long stairs to the south east.\n6. Through the door, turn right and follow the long hallway southeast to (M-8), past the Moongate. This is where the ??? is to spawn the NM, on the ground in front of an inaccessible tunnel entrance.\n7. This fight is against Eldhrimnir, a magic pot. Once you kill it, re-examine the ??? to receive the key item Annals of Truth.\n8. Go back and speak with Kuroido-Moido to receive your reward.',
        notes = nil,
    },
