        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Mashuu-Ajuu who will give you a bag of Herb Seeds and ask you to plant them.\n2. You can plant the seeds and grow them into a Deathball or Sobbing Fungus, or you can just purchase them off the Auction House.\n   - The Sobbing Fungas can also be bought at Soupox in Leafallia for 60 Gil.\n3. Trading Mashuu-Ajuu a Deathball will reward you with a Stationery Set and 700 gil.\n4. Trading Mashuu-Ajuu a Sobbing Fungus will reward you with a Stationery Set and 500 gil.\n5. Repeat attempts will not reward the Stationary Set.\n6. Repeat attempts require trading a Sobbing Fungus.\n7. You will not get any more Herb Seeds other than the first time.\n8. If you set your home point to Windurst and have the appropriate Rhapsodies Key Item, this will only cost 160 by using a BLM Warp. Profiting 340 Gil each turn-in by buying the Sobbing Fungus from Soupox.',
