        start_zone = 'Port Windurst',
        start_pos = 'G-5',
        description = 'To help the Joker Cardian escape far away from Windurst, the Star Onion Brigade wants you to have Pichichi\'s mother, Chamama, make him an "Invisible Man Sticker."',
