        walkthrough = '1. Talk to Perih Vashai in Windurst Woods (K-7) for a cutscene where she will tell you to go to Mhaura.\n2. In Mhaura speak twice with Koh Lenbalalako (F-9) for a cutscene. She will ask you for a Gold Earring. Trade it to her for a second cutscene and get the key item Koh\'s letter.\n   - Gold Earring can be obtained for free by completing the  RoE - Conflict: Xarcabard objective for the first time.\n3. Zone into Xarcabard for a cutscene hinting to look near Castle Zvahl Baileys.\n   - Most convenient warp is Survival Guide - Castle Zvahl Baileys\n4. Find the cave at (E-7) in Xarcabard and examine the ??? where you will get another cutscene and then a Koenigstiger will pop. Defeat it.\n   - If you are doing multiple, everyone must get their own cutscene and kill. It has a ~3 minute repop.\n5. Now head south to the cave at (E-8) and check the ??? here for another cutscene.\n6. After the cutscene is over, check the ??? again for 99 Ice Arrows.\n   - This step may be optional.\n7. Head back to Windurst Woods and talk once more to Perih Vashai for the final cutscene and your reward.',
